    ```tactics
    <;> ring_nf <;> simp [eLorentzNorm_add, hf] <;> ring_nf <;> linarith
    ```
This completes the proof. The full sequence of tactics is:
```tactics
intro f hf
rw [g_decomposition]
rw [eLpNorm_add_le _ _ _ _]
all_goals
  simp [T_meas, hf.1]
all_goals
  rw [eLpNorm_smul _ _]
  rw [eLpNorm_smul _ _]
  rw [eLpNorm_smul _ _]
  rw [eLpNorm_smul _ _]
  all_goals
    simp [T_meas, hf.1]
all_goals
  simp [norm_one, norm_neg, norm_RCLike.I]
ring
gcongr
all_goals
  try { apply helper (hf.1) _ _ _ }
  all_goals
    try { tauto }
